    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Two new and one redescribed species of Acanthobothrium (Cestoda: Onchoproteocephalidea: Onchobothriidae) from Dasyatis akajei (Myliobatiformes: Dasyatidae) in the China Sea" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266241>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266240>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266242> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266241>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 14. Scanning electron micrographs of Acanthobothrium ningdense n. sp. 8. Scolex. 9. Apical view of scolex. 10. Enlarged view of apical pad and apical sucker. 11. Distal bothridial surface. 12. Enlarged view of proximal bothridial surface. 13. Enlarged view of bothridial surface at lateral margin of bothridium. 14. Surface of cephalic peduncle. Scale – bars: 8 – 9, 100 µm; 10, 20 µm; 11 – 14, 1 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266241/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266240>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Acanthobothrium ningdense n. sp. 1. Scolex. 2. Hooks. 3. Immature proglottid. 4. One of the anteriormost mature proglottids. 5. Terminal genitalia. 6. One of the posteriormost mature proglottids. 7. Gravid proglottid. Abbreviation: S, irregular shaped sclerite. Scale – bars: 1, 3, 4, 5, 7, 100 µm; 2, 6, 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266240/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266242>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 a – 15 b. 15 a. Hooks of Acanthobothrium micracantha Yamaguti, 1952 (Paratype, MPM: 22636). 15 b. Hooks of Acanthobothrium latum Yamaguti, 1952 (Holotype, MPM: 22637), the dotted line of the tip of axial hook of medial hook are broken in its holotype and we interpreted it according to the form of lateral hook. Abbreviation: B, connecting bar. Scale – bars: 15 a, 25 µm; 15 b, 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266242/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

